{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/use-the-some-method-to-check-that-any-elements-in-an-array-meet-a-criteria","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"functional-programming","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi putanju `some` da proveriš da li svi elementi u nizu podataka zadovoljavaju kriterijume.","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Funkcija <code>some</code> radi sa nizovima podataka da proveri da li bilo koji element prolazi kroz određeni test. Vraća vrednost tačno ili netačno - <code>true</code> ako bilo koja vrednost ispunjava kriterijume, <code>false</code> inače.</p>\n<p>Na primer, sledeći kod proverava da li je bilo koji element u redovima podataka <code>numbers</code> manji od 10:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const numbers = [10, 50, 8, 220, 110, 11];\r\n\r\nnumbers.some(function(currentValue) {\r\n  return currentValue &#x3C; 10;\r\n});\n</code></pre>\n<p>Putanja za <code>some</code> koristiće <code>true</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7dab367417b2b2512b6f","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristi putanju <code>some</code> unutar funkcije <code>checkPositive</code> da proveri da li je bilo koji element u <code>arr</code> pozitivan. Funkcija bi trebalo da vrati vrednost tačno ili netačno.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301314,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/use-the-some-method-to-check-that-any-elements-in-an-array-meet-a-criteria"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function checkPositive(arr) {\r\n  // Only change code below this line\r\n\